## –ë—ã—Å—Ç—Ä—ã–π —Å—Ç–∞—Ä—Ç

```python
import asyncio
from kwork import Kwork

async def main():
    api = Kwork(login="login", password="password")

    try:
        me = await api.get_me()
        print(f"{me.username} | {me.free_amount} {me.currency}")
    finally:
        await api.close()

asyncio.run(main())
```

